# FormForge Project Overview

FormForge is a form builder application with the following structure:

## Frontend
- React-based application with TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- React Router for navigation
- React Query for data fetching

## Backend
- GraphQL API using Pothos
- Drizzle ORM for database operations
- PostgreSQL database (via PGLite for development)
- Lucia for authentication

## Key Directories
- `/src/components`: React components
- `/src/context`: React context providers
- `/src/lib`: Core libraries and utilities
  - `/lib/graphql`: GraphQL schema, resolvers, and types
  - `/lib/schema`: Database schema definitions
  - `/lib/migrations`: Database migrations
- `/src/pages`: React page components
- `/src/server`: API server code
